text:
Since it's a costume that exposes my stomach,
I'm feeling a bit hesitant...

Did you dislike it?!
I can discuss changing the design──

No, um, it's not that I dislike it... It's just that I never imagined
I would wear this kind of costume, so it's more like──
It's just the feeling of realizing, "I'm an idol", you know...?
I'm sorry, but I'm fine, really...!
